songs.title: Intro
songs.lyrics:
"I could set you free"
"But you won't..."
"It's a possibility"
"You can kill me"
"That is another one"
"But you'd rather see me crawl"
"That's who I am. Who are you?"
"I'm the one you can't break. I'm what ya been afraid of all your life"
"I'm afraid of nothing"
"You're afraid of failing. I'm not gonna play your games"
